edu.jhu.pha.helpers.adqlhelper
Class AdqlConverter

java.lang.Object
  edu.jhu.pha.helpers.adqlhelper.AdqlConverter

public class AdqlConverter
extends java.lang.Object

Converts Adql from earlier XML schema versions to version 2.0. Replaces ConvertADQL which was suitable only for a test environment.

See Also:
AdqlParserSV, org.astrogrid.adql.AdqlParserSVNC
